                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px;font-weight:700;">School Surveys</span>With a view to know the present status of the schools of Charotar region through data collection, a survey was carried out. The survey consisted of data about the school infrastructure, strength of students in each class, number of teachers etc. Till date total 66 schools have been surveyed. Total 22930 students of standard 1 to 12 from 66 schools within the span of 50 kilometers have been covered till date.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <!--<li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 18px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #3db166 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
